P5 - Log Explosion Incident Summary

1. Create project directory

mkdir P5-Log-Explosion-Lab
cd P5-Log-Explosion-Lab

2. Check disk usage

df -h

3. Create a log file

touch app.log

4. Simulate log explosion

yes "ERROR application failure detected" >> app.log

(The command continuously writes log entries)

5. Check log size

du -sh *

Example output:
61G app.log

6. Resolve the issue by clearing the log

truncate -s 0 app.log

7. Verify disk usage

df -h
